The author typesets the website in ◊reference["https://docs.racket-lang.org/pollen/"]{Pollen}, a ◊reference["https://racket-lang.org/"]{Racket} library by ◊reference["http://typographyforlawyers.com/about.html"]{Matthew Butterick}. The CSS comes from a ◊reference["/software/css-expr/"]{◊code{css-expr}} source, a language designed by the author. The software for drawing vector graphics is ◊reference["https://inkscape.org/"]{Inkscape}. The serif font is ◊reference["http://practicaltypography.com/charter.html"]{Charter}, by ◊reference["https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matthew_Carter"]{Matthew Carter}, from Bitstream. The monospaced font is ◊reference["https://mozilla.github.io/Fira/"]{Fira Mono}, by ◊reference["http://bboxtype.com"]{bBoxType} for ◊reference["https://www.mozilla.org/"]{Mozilla}. Illustrations come from ◊reference["http://fontawesome.io/"]{Font Awesome}, by Dave Gandy and ◊reference["https://fortawesome.com/"]{Fort Awesome}; the ◊reference["https://github.com/elementary/icons"]{Elementary icon set}, by ◊reference["https://elementary.io/"]{elementary OS}; ◊reference["https://github.com/emojione/emojione/tree/2.2.7"]{EmojiOne 2.2.7}, by ◊reference["https://www.emojione.com/"]{EmojiOne}; ◊reference["https://github.com/google/material-design-icons"]{Material Design} icons and ◊reference["https://github.com/googlei18n/noto-emoji"]{Noto Emoji} by ◊reference["https://google.github.io/material-design-icons/"]{Google}; and ◊reference["https://github.com/twitter/twemoji"]{Twemoji} by ◊reference["https://twitter.github.io/twemoji/"]{Twitter}. Colors come from the ◊reference["http://ethanschoonover.com/solarized"]{Solarized} colorscheme, by ◊reference["http://ethanschoonover.com/"]{Ethan Schoonover}. Syntax highlighting uses ◊reference["http://pygments.org/"]{Pygments}. The page layout draws from the works of ◊reference["http://typographyforlawyers.com/about.html"]{Matthew Butterick} and ◊reference["https://www.edwardtufte.com/"]{Edward Rolf Tufte}.